banner.subtitle: Moqod will hire, set up and manage your own team of software developers in Ukraine. Any technology stack, excellent skills, fully managed, flexible contract. Moqod guarantees best candidates that match your requirements.
banner.title: Fully managed remote teams of software developers employed for your projects

list.text: It is important for our recruitment to understand the skills, level and expertise you are looking for. What is your project about? What is the team like? What will be the person’s daily tasks and roles?
list.title: Customer provides us with job description and requirements

list.text: We identify the right candidate based on your criteria within our network. We conduct initial screening interview to evaluate soft skills, language and motivation.
list.title: Screening

list.text: Our technical experts conduct a detailed interview with the candidates to estimate his knowledge and professional skills. An evaluation report is provided to customers.
list.title: Initial tech review

list.text: Matching candidates are advised for customer interview. You speak with the candidates and see if there is a match with your culture, values and expectations. On-site trip to Kiev or your office can be organized.
list.title: Customer interview

list.text: We know the market prices and can help you make the right decision. Time to sign the papers!
list.title: Job offer and contract

list.text: We identify the right candidate based on your criteria within our network. We conduct initial screening interview to evaluate soft skills, language and motivation.
list.title: Ongoing reviews

list.text: Your remote team at Moqod is literally your staff under our umbrella of financial, legal and management support.
list.title: Financial and legal support

list.text: Moqod ensures reliable communication between the customer and his team. We set up an infrastructure for language classes and cultural exchange.
list.title: Cultural and language trainings

list.text: With our internal expertise Moqod helps to identify the right candidates matching the skillset and ensure career growth.
list.title: Process and technology review

list.text: Soft skills matter! Good team work and results are reached by the right combination of characters.
list.title: Personality matching
